        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4734",
        "content": "Afterward Christ came, saying, \"I am born of the Holy Spirit.\" Though it is now easy for the Christians to believe this assertion, at that time it was very difficult.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
