        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4734",
        "content": "Moreover, He brought to humanity the glad tidings of universal peace, and spread abroad teachings which were not for Israel alone but were for the general happiness of the whole human race.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
